From: Fuat Keceli <fuat.keceli@intel.com>
Date: Fri, 9 Oct 2020 08:54:30 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 2/4] Changed LAinc/lib to the correct paths and -openmp flag
 to -fiopenmp

